{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libuv/libuv/issues/424","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libuv/libuv","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libuv/libuv/issues/424/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libuv/libuv/issues/424/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libuv/libuv/issues/424/events","html_url":"https://github.com/libuv/libuv/issues/424","id":93163505,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU5MzE2MzUwNQ==","number":424,"title":"Windows consoles with non-default colors","user":{"login":"mcnameej","id":173804,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3MzgwNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/173804?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej","html_url":"https://github.com/mcnameej","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mcnameej/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2015-07-06T01:00:32Z","updated_at":"2015-07-10T03:28:00Z","closed_at":"2015-07-10T03:28:00Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"The ANSI terminal emulation code in src/win/tty.c assumes the console is using Windows default colors (white text on a black background). This results in a somewhat ugly output on consoles using different colors **and** it leaves the console in a bad state, affecting programs that run afterwards.\n\nNote: The problem only occurs after some attempt is made to change the text color; programs that display only plain text are fine.\n\n**Example:**\n\nEverything looks good if the console text is white on black...\n\n![screen shot - black background](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/173804/8514031/ab228384-2348-11e5-8942-0773913a62c3.png)\n\n...but not so good with other colors (the console was set to bright white on blue in this example)...\n\n![screen shot - blue background](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/173804/8514033/aeb894de-2348-11e5-97e0-fc48fd92647c.png)\n\n(Note: The error shown in the screen shots is irrelevant; it was was deliberately created to demonstrate the color problem.)\n","closed_by":{"login":"piscisaureus","id":218257,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIxODI1Nw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/218257?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus","html_url":"https://github.com/piscisaureus","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/piscisaureus/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libuv/libuv/issu